data.description: Custom 3900+ sqft home with 3 levels in the upper valley. Enter into the main level from the driveway or garage to an open kitchen, dining and living areas that expand out to the covered deck. You will appreciate the extra-large island, wet bar and desk area in the kitchen. Enjoy going right out of the dining room to the recently refinished covered deck with the lights and sound system in place.  Upstairs is the primary bedroom with large closet that passes thru to the updated primary bathroom with a soaking tub and vanity area. Laundry room and 2nd bedroom are also upstairs. The daylight basement has all the extra space needed with the 3rd bedroom and extra living space with new fresh carpet, sound system and heated floors even under the carpet! You can find plenty of storage down there as well with access to the outside. Enjoy going down the lighted path to your own fire pit area. Plenty of parking with the double car attached garage and large graveled driveway. On demand water heaters, heated floors throughout the main level and basement including storage area, newer mini split (2020), updated front entry concrete and pillars (2020) all make this home a great place to live.
